title: [COMPLETE] Scheduled Maintenance - 15/10/2015
body:
Hi all,

We'll be doing some planned maintenance to our game server network during off-peak.  As a precaution, we'll be disabling Ranked from 0400am - 0600am AEDT (Sydney time) on the 15th Oct 2015.   This is just a precaution, as we don't want to risk any precious LP!  Normal queues will remain active during this time.

If you've got any questions, let me know.

-Mindstar
